          The <em>transpose of the matrix</em>
    <idx><h>transpose</h></idx>
    <idx><h>matrix</h><h>transpose</h></idx> <m>\boldsymbol{A}</m>, denoted by  <m>A^T</m>, is the  2 by 2  matrix over  <m>\mathbb{R}</m> defined by
          <me>
